{"tid":1531102,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"致想跳閘又唔敢跳既人","createTime":"2019-09-02T06:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T08:31:16.000Z","uid":154176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"af785f8b091e0663323e5b7b0f7d14aa97895046","tid":1531102,"uid":154176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:26:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我諗依家好多人拍卡之前都有呢個想頭<br />\n但就係差嗰一步 突破唔到心理關口<br />\n驚跳完個下唔知會唔會比人捉 又閉路電視等等<br />\n<br />\n但我同你講 <span style=\"color: red;\">係冇事發生</span><br />\n掉轉角度 你係職員 如果每日平均一個鐘<br />\n十幾條友跳 你會努力去捉 定係扮睇唔到？<br />\n<br />\n但呢個就係問題 <br />\n<br />\n平均一個鐘可唔可以有十人以上跳？<br />\n就係睇你夠唔夠膽 你係咪其中一個<br />\n全港得一個人跳就危險 十個二十個 一百個<br />\n<br />\n人類係群居動物 肯齊心就搞掂。<br />\n<br />\n當你想跳 但唔敢跳既時候諗下<br />\n拍卡比錢港鐵 但每年加錢車費 壞車頻密<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同黑警勾結 關站放狗打人 流哂血</span><br />\n<br />\n你真係覺得要盡市民責任 比交通費用？<br />\n<br />\n同埋我有個提議 大膽既 真係可以見多人 <br />\n帶頭跳 但其他人<span style=\"color: red;\">請跟上，唔好再驚</span><br />\n突破心理關口一次 你就唔會再驚 <br />\n<br />\n同埋請身邊唔敢跳閘既人<br />\n唔好係咁望 指指點點咁 <br />\n你咁樣係會令初次跳既人感到好大壓力<br />\n下次唔再夠膽跳<br />\n<br />\n都忍得港鐵耐啦掛<br />\n大家香港人一條心 比啲勇氣啦 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">加油 香港人</span></span>"},{"pid":"64d26cbc4dc911ec9186648ca569fd78528bce6f","tid":1531102,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"建議申請星期一至五遊行，九龍灣同中環，等黨鐵助攻<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1500513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1500513</a>"},{"pid":"27a993aab01ce3ab317514186ec3f63ad52d2a13","tid":1531102,"uid":260852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"唔敢跳個啲可以拍卡再跳閘 一來比後面個個人有得入 二來又可以掩飾真正跳閘既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257ed514ec0122424736a05f0b4413b5d4d98aaa","tid":1531102,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>未爛未拆 咁樣入！</strong></span></span><br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmZ8JRV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmZ8JRV.gif&h=d48b36ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQ6rr7H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQ6rr7H.gif&h=2e882f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}